        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3010419753" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16311590247188651195">At over 36 hours on audio,<br/>Perhaps this sort of long form historical novel is not for everyone. It is the sad story of the 18 years civil war between Stephen and Maud. If you read the Brother Cadfael novels you will likely enjoy reading more about this war and the people who inhabited it. Sharon Kay Penman is a master at characterization and capturing a time. Writing one novel like this is astounding; writing as many as she has is almost incomprehensible.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


